    Client -->|"HTTP/8090<br/>plaintext<br/>Auth: Bearer token<br/>(pass-through)"| Gateway
    Gateway -->|"HTTP or HTTPS/8085<br/>Optional mTLS (TLS 1.2+)<br/>Auth: mTLS cert +<br/>forwarded Authorization +<br/>x-forwarded-* headers"| Orchestrator

    %% Styling
